<div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto my-12 bg-white p-8 rounded shadow">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="mb-4">
    This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal data when you use our Todo App.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">1. What Data We Collect</h2>
  <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4">
    <li>Account information: username, password (hashed)</li>
    <li>Todo items you create</li>
    <li>Session data (for login and security)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">2. Why We Collect Data</h2>
  <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4">
    <li>To provide and secure your account</li>
    <li>To save and display your todo items</li>
    <li>To manage your login session</li>
    <li>To improve your experience</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
  <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4">
    <li>We use your data only to operate the Todo App and provide its features</li>
    <li>We do not sell or share your data with third parties</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">4. How Long We Store Data</h2>
  <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4">
    <li>Your account and todos are stored until you delete your account</li>
    <li>Session data is kept only as long as your session is active</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">5. Your Rights</h2>
  <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4">
    <li>You can view, edit, or delete your account and todos at any time</li>
    <li>You can request access to your data</li>
    <li>You can request deletion of your account and all associated data</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">6. Contact</h2>
  <p class="mb-4">
    If you have questions about your data or this policy, contact us at <a href="mailto:admin@example.com" class="text-blue-600 underline">admin@example.com</a>.
  </p>

  <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2">7. Changes</h2>
  <p>
    We may update this policy. We will notify you of significant changes.
  </p>
</div>
